* removing isort
* fixed typo
* removing isort
* added scene tests, cleaned up
* mocking pytest.gl
* mocking application
* correctly mocking pyglet gl
* trying inline import
* not importing escape directly from arcade
* mocking out pyglet
* try not to load arcade
* added scene test
